          "html": "<table>\n  <tr>\n    <th colspan=\"2\">Algorithm 1 The training algorithm of PEAGNN</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>1:</td>\n    <td>Input: A HIN $G$ , number of iterations $M$ , $\\gamma$ -metapaths</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>2:</td>\n    <td>Output: Learned node representations $\\mathbf{E}$ , a prediction model $\\tilde{r}$ </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>3:</td>\n    <td>for $i = 1$ to $M$ do</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>4:</td>\n    <td>Sample a batch $\\mathcal{B}$ of training user-item interactions</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>5:</td>\n    <td>Construct the CSGs of $\\mathcal{B}$ as illustrated in the figure 1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>6:</td>\n    <td>Sample the Metapath-aware Subgraphs from the constructed CSGs with the given $\\gamma$ metapaths</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>7:</td>\n    <td>Perform step-wise information propagation over the Metapath-aware Subgraphs as per eqs. 1 and 2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>8:</td>\n    <td>For each node, obtain the metapath-aware node representation by fusing the representation from $\\gamma$ metapaths with attention factors (see eqs. 4 and 5)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>9:</td>\n    <td>Use the graph-level representation to calculate the interaction scores of user $u$ and item $i$ via eqs. 6 and 7</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>10:</td>\n    <td>Compute the training loss with eqs. 8, 9 and 10 and update model parameters</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>11:</td>\n    <td>end for</td>\n  </tr>\n</table>"
        }
      ]
